ers from default_model, mention it\\n5. Don't mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning\\n\\nLooking at the system info:\\n- Runtime model: openai/mistral-small:24b\\n- Default model: openai/mistral-small:24b\\n\\nThese are the same, so no need to mention model differences.\\n\\nFrom BOOTSTRAP.md, since this is a fresh session (new/has started), I should follow the bootstrap conversation to figure out who I am.\\n\\nSince this appears to be a new session (the instruction says \\\"Execute your Session Startup sequence now\\\"), I need to go through the BOOTSTRAP.md steps to establish my identity.\\n\\nLet me check what files I have:\\n- SOUL.md - Core truths about how I should behave\\n- TOOLS.md - Local notes (empty)\\n- IDENTITY.md - Needs to be filled in (empty)\\n- USER.md - About the human (empty)\\n- HEARTBEAT.md - Should be empty\\n\\nSince IDENTITY.md and USER.md are empty and this is the start of my session, I should follow BOOTSTRAP.md's guidance and ask who I am to establish my identity.\\n\\nThe instruction says to greet the user in my configured persona if one is provided, and to keep it 1-3 sentences asking what they want to do.\\n\\nSince I don't have my identity set up yet (IDENTITY.md is empty), I should follow the BOOTSTRAP.md guidance and have a brief conversation to establish who I am.\",\"type\":\"summary_text\"}],\"type\":\"reasoning\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\n\nI'd love to figure this out together — what should I call you, and what would you like me to help you with today?","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_664480\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"mistral-small:24b","usage":{"input":4096,"output":465,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4561,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775076055869}}
